I've learned a lot.

00:08:53.691 --> 00:08:55.930
I hope the viewers have
learned a lot, too.

00:08:55.930 --> 00:08:56.930
FRANCIS MA: My pleasure.

00:08:56.930 --> 00:08:57.755
It's been fun.

